<h2 id="verification">Verification</h2>

<h3 id="verification-tiers">What are the verifications tiers?</h3>

<p>The law requires we know who you are and where you are. The more services you need, the more information we need to collect from you.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Tier 0 - you can look around but you can't deposit, withdraw or make any trades.</li>
  <li>Tier 1 - you can deposit, withdraw and trade in digital currency only. You cannot do bank deposits or withdrawals.</li>
  <li>Tier 2 - you can deposit, withdraw and trade in both digital currency and national currency. Bank deposits and withdrawals are available at this tier and higher.</li>
  <li>Tier 3 - like Tier 2 but with higher funding limits.</li>
  <li>Tier 4 - like Tier 3 but with even higher funding limits.</li>
</ul>

<p>Processing - if your verification application has been "Processing" for more than 30 minutes, this means our automated systems could not process it completely and it's waiting for manual review. We'll review your application as soon as we can, but there may be many people in line ahead of you, so you may have to wait many days. Usually, however, it only takes a few days at most.</p>

